Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.16,0:00:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前情提要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Previously on Foundation…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.08,0:00:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝国将灭亡 我们做的一切都无法避免它的到来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Empire will fall. Nothing we do can prevent this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.92,0:00:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威胁和平 就要付出沉重代价\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Threaten the peace and pay a dear price.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.59,0:00:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉在世和亡故的人 你们未能拯救他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell the living and the dead you failed to save them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.89,0:00:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们称之为“穹窿”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They called it "the Vault."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.43,0:00:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-波利 -波利 回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Poly! -Poly, come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.52,0:00:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想见幽灵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wanna see the ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.93,0:00:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它在周围投射了一个阻止人们靠近的力场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It projected a field designed to keep people away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.90,0:00:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从来没有人突破空域\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothing has ever gotten through the null field,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.40,0:00:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后也不会有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and nothing ever will.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.49,0:01:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（改编自艾萨克阿西莫夫的小说）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.21,0:02:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个世界都有幽灵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Every world has ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.26,0:02:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每所房子都有幽灵出没\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And every house is haunted by them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.93,0:02:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是帝国宫殿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even the palace of the Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.77,0:02:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是帝国宫殿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Especially the palace of the Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.31,0:02:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（400年前）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.94,0:02:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪了 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.44,0:02:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和系统程序员在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}With the systems programmers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.94,0:02:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最近和他们在一起的时间 多于和我在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lately you've been with them more than with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.03,0:02:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（克里昂一世）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.11,0:02:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给他们安排了一项艰巨的任务\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've set them a large task.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.08,0:02:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有必要找人替换他们吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Should we look to replace them?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.74,0:02:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们能完成任务的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They'll see it through.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.12,0:02:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德默泽尔 我能信赖你吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can count on you, Demerzel?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.71,0:02:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确保任务完成 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To see it through?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.21,0:02:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 克里昂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course, Cleon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅是完成任务\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And not just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.84,0:02:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有其他一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.63,0:02:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总是认为在我走后你会留下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I always assumed you'd stay on after I was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.09,0:02:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但接近人生的尾声 我才意识到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But it occurred to me, in the near-darkness of my life…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.68,0:02:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何事情都不是理所应当的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I shouldn't take anything for granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.23,0:02:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对帝国忠心不二\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm loyal to the Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.15,0:02:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 但帝国会对你忠心不二吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, but will the Empire be loyal to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.23,0:03:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它对你的同类从未仁慈过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It hasn't always shown benevolence to your kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.74,0:03:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你变得多愁善感了 几乎接近伤感\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're becoming sentimental, verging on maudlin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我即将死去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I'm dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.12,0:03:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我留下的是一个支离破碎的世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I'm leaving everything in pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.54,0:03:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对继任者不满意吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you unhappy with your successor?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.34,0:03:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们仍可以考虑婚姻和子嗣这一方案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can still revisit the idea of marriage and an heir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.59,0:03:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德默泽尔 毕竟你不是人类 也可能正因如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Demerzel, for all you are, and maybe because of it…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.35,0:03:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些事情 你永远不会理解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}there are things you will never know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.89,0:03:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许有一天我会理解死亡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I may someday know death.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.35,0:03:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.31,0:03:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我认为你不会觉得死亡来得太快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I doubt you will feel it arrived too soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.15,0:03:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该目睹星桥的建成\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I should have seen the completion of the Star Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我的头脑 我的眼睛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Me. My mind. My eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.83,0:03:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们应该一起乘车上轨道平台\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We should have ridden up to the orbital platform together
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.08,0:03:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俯瞰我们所创造的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and looked down on all that we had made.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.88,0:04:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有那一天的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And one day we will.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.01,0:04:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的王朝将永远延续\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your continuity is assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.84,0:04:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（400年后）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.56,0:04:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你常常想他吗  -你知道我是怎么样的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Do you think of him often? -You know the way I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.64,0:04:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从不忘记任何事或任何人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't forget anything or anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.15,0:04:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（星桥爆炸事件19年后）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.98,0:04:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大帝永远在我心上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Empire is always on my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.07,0:04:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平台的轨道运行正加速失效\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The platform's orbit is dying at an accelerated rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少物理学家是这么说的 他们担心它会掉下来砸到自己头上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or so say the physicists, who worry it'll just fall on their heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.70,0:04:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担心这种事是他们的职责\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Their job is to worry over those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.66,0:04:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是我们的职责吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is it not ours?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.50,0:04:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许仍是你的 但这已经不归我管了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps it is still yours, but no longer mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不归他管了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as it is no longer his.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.55,0:04:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何度过最后一天由你决定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How you spend this last day is up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.85,0:04:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一个你都不一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Every one of you is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.14,0:04:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于这点 我很怀疑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Somehow I doubt that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.27,0:05:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但多谢你尝试 让我在临死之时感到自己是独一无二的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But thank you for trying to make me feel unique as I shuffle off the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.99,0:05:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对他来说 这个过程最困难\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was hardest on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.28,0:05:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时能即位的只有婴儿黎明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He only had the infant Dawn to place on the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.45,0:05:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个有着他双眼的婴儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A baby with his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.41,0:05:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在任何方面都与他一模一样 但仍只是个婴儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Identical in every respect, but a baby nonetheless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.25,0:05:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我想到他时 那是我所想到的画面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When I think of him, that's what I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也有你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He also had you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.72,0:05:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大帝 请去见伊兰师傅 他在等待你的最后试衣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please see Master Ilan, Empire. He's waiting for your final fitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.53,0:05:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始吧 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.33,0:06:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,细节是完美的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The details, they're perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用什么缝边 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For the pick stitching?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.05,0:06:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翡翠吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The jade, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.64,0:06:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shoo, shoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.23,0:06:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 大帝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am sorry, Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.61,0:06:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我瘦了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have lost weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.95,0:06:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-您的身型一定… -我在萎缩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I am sure your frame is-- -I am shrinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.41,0:06:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我与世界的距离变得遥远\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The world is beginning to see me from a distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.16,0:06:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这套衣服令人惊叹 伊兰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The garment is singular, Ilan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.71,0:06:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身穿这套衣服升天是我的荣幸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It will be a privilege to wear it at my ascension.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.00,0:06:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 大帝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.88,0:06:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们继续吧 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Shall we finish the job? -Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.80,0:07:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊兰 给这姑娘一个机会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ilan, let's let the girl have the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.57,0:07:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄昏兄弟 我不知道你在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Brother Dusk? I didn't know you'd be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安纳克里昂 狄斯比斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anacreon. Thespis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.42,0:07:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道在我走后 你是否还会说起他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wonder if you will speak of them after I'm gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.09,0:07:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们打败了蛮族 将他们驱逐出帝国\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have broken the barbarians. Cast them adrift.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.55,0:07:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你希望我们说出什么你还没说过的话吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What would you have us say that you haven't said?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.09,0:07:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 我还在决定 有哪些话是我还没说但该说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know. I'm still trying to decide what to say that I haven't said.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.43,0:07:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于外围星域吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}About the Outer Reach?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.77,0:07:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于任何事 关于我们是否 真的有权控制这一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}About anything. About whether any of this is truly within our power to control.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.56,0:07:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说话的机会已不多 我不想浪费它们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}However many words I have left, I would hate to waste them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.48,0:07:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说起外围星域的时候已经是在浪费了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You waste them when you speak of the Outer Reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.69,0:07:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说到谢顿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I speak of Seldon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.03,0:07:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个已死去多时的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A man long dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.70,0:07:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,且很快就被遗忘的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And soon forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.82,0:08:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那意味着他的言语 对这个帝国已经毫无价值了吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Does that mean his words have no more worth in this Empire?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.45,0:08:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄弟 帝国很强大…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Brother, the Empire is strong--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.92,0:08:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里昂一世的功业\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cleon I's legacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.34,0:08:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道有没有办法拯救它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wonder if there's a way to save it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.17,0:08:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用推进器稳定它 将它送到星系更深处 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stabilize it with propulsive lifts? Push it out into the heavens?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.14,0:08:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To what end?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.39,0:08:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不摧毁克里昂一世梦想中仅存的部分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To the end that we not destroy the last remnants of Cleon I's dream
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.68,0:08:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们并没有梦想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for lack of our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄昏兄弟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Brother Dusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里昂一世的伟大梦想是我们 不是星桥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We are the great dream of Cleon I, not the Star Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.75,0:08:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦想者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The dreamer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.92,0:08:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The scholar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.22,0:08:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炼金术师\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The alchemist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.97,0:09:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（克里昂11世 画家）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.26,0:09:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.35,0:09:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（克里昂一世 梦想者）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.53,0:09:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一辈子都尝试模仿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've tried my whole life,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.12,0:09:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我从没成功做出这个表情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I don't think I've ever been able to make that face.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.12,0:09:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 你的兄弟们为你准备了最后的礼物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come. Your brothers have your last gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.75,0:09:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想感谢你们 我的兄弟 为我准备了这顿丰盛的美餐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I would like to thank you, Brothers, for this beautiful meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.63,0:09:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一口都能尝出你们的用心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can taste the care you put into each bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.97,0:09:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很感激你们抽时间费心这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your time and your attention is deeply appreciated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.39,0:09:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客气 兄弟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're very welcome, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.06,0:09:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这不是礼物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But this is not the gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.82,0:10:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到川陀 帝国中心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Welcome to Trantor, the eye of the Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.95,0:10:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经太久了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's been so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.49,0:10:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他真伟岸 对吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was glorious, wasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.33,0:10:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心怀尊敬 享受和平\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please respect and enjoy the peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.08,0:10:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.95,0:10:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们将建造更伟大的事物 以纪念他 也是为了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And we will build something greater in his honor. For you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心怀尊敬 享受和平\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please respect and enjoy the peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.72,0:12:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能来这里 你是知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can't be here. You know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.60,0:12:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不可能是第一个 想看自己最年幼时样貌的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't be the first one who wanted to see my youngest self.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.19,0:12:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这正是我们立下这条规则的原因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which is why we made the rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.23,0:12:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从没听过这首歌 还是说听过 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've never heard that song before. Or have I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.87,0:12:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得大帝如此爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No wonder the Empire loves you so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.58,0:13:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我发现自己无法将那孩子视作无辜者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I find I cannot quite look on that child as an innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算谢顿是错的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even if Seldon wasn't right…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.17,0:13:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也是不合乎自然规律的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}there is something unnatural in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.51,0:13:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You must go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.97,0:13:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该休息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You should rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.73,0:13:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着自己出生 感觉真奇怪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Strange, watching yourself being born.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.14,0:14:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡吧 明天见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sleep. I'll see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.73,0:14:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今晚看到你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I saw you tonight…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.27,0:14:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在看我们的第一位兄弟出现在星桥遗址\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}watching our first brother in the old Star Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.52,0:14:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还不够吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are we not enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.28,0:14:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你想念他的原因吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that why you miss him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.70,0:14:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 亲爱的兄弟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, no, sweet brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.24,0:15:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你就足够了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.55,0:15:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是你们总会离我而去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's just that you always leave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.69,0:16:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已成长为伟大的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have grown into our greatness,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.61,0:16:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎明兄弟现在已是白昼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Brother Dawn, now Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.67,0:16:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 黄昏兄弟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Brother Dusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.64,0:16:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的黎明刚醒来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the new Dawn, just awoken.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.69,0:16:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你将有漫长而美丽的未来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have a long, beautiful day ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.82,0:17:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗兄弟 是时候了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Brother Darkness, it's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.30,0:17:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由你继续完成梦想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The dream lives on in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.13,0:17:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你让它生机勃勃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because you kept it alive in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.66,0:17:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shh. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.29,0:17:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会有事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.63,0:17:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都安好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everything is all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:17:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.76,0:18:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么不对劲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Something's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.15,0:18:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德默泽尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Demerzel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.45,0:18:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从不忘记任何事或任何人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't forget anything or anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.58,0:18:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大帝永远都在我心上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Empire is always on my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.10,0:19:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活着即意味着与幽灵相伴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To be alive is to know ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.74,0:19:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果用心听 我们能听见幽灵的低语\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We hear their whispers if we listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（17年后）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.16,0:19:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都笼罩在预言的阴影下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We are haunted by prophets, all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.04,0:19:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（克里昂14世）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.13,0:20:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎明兄弟 你确定要抹去壁画吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you certain you want it erased, Brother Dawn?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.80,0:20:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.63,0:20:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它对我来说已过时了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've outgrown it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.72,0:20:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们忽视亡者 让自己陷于险境\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We ignore the dead at our peril.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.60,0:20:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随着帝国历经了另一代克里昂的统治后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And as Empire cycled through a generation of Cleons,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.02,0:20:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基地开始对端点星进行殖民\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the Foundation began colonizing Terminus.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.07,0:20:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝国低估了哈里 我们都低估他了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Empire underestimated Hari. We all did.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.12,0:20:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里成功预测 克里昂将流放他 而不是处决\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hari had predicted the Cleons would opt for exile over execution…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.08,0:20:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他门下信徒的终点将是端点星\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that his followers' end point would be Terminus.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.43,0:20:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们到达后的每个方面 都已经预测好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Every aspect of their arrival was predetermined…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.85,0:21:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殖民者何时着陆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when the colonists would land…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.03,0:21:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们在何处建造哨站\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}where they would build their outpost.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.42,0:21:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以可以想象他们有多惊讶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So imagine their surprise
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.84,0:21:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当他们发现那里已经有一个建筑了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when they discovered that something else was already there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.06,0:21:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以谢顿之名啊 那是什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What in Seldon's name is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.62,0:22:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勘测结果里没有这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It wasn't in the surveys.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.29,0:22:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们应该回去吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Should we go back?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.88,0:22:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回哪里 马莉  从一开始这就是一趟单程的旅程\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go back where, Mari? This was always a one-way journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.75,0:22:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我去看看 -不行 我们一起去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I'll check it out. -No. We go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.02,0:22:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劳莉 你还好吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lowre, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.93,0:22:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-没事… -走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Yeah. Yeah. -Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.10,0:22:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我只是有点头晕 -走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I'm just a little light-headed. -Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.15,0:22:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.99,0:22:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿巴斯 往回走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Abbas! Get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.58,0:22:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们称它为穹窿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It became known as the Vault.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.84,0:22:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数十年来流传着无数关于穹窿的传说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And over the decades, countless myths grew up around it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.01,0:22:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人说它是外星人留下的古老文物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was an ancient artifact left by aliens…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.60,0:23:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有人说它是克里昂们建造的监控站\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a surveillance outpost sent ahead by the Cleons.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.48,0:23:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有殖民者都很清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All the settlers knew for certain
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.69,0:23:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穹窿不让任何人靠近\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}was that the Vault wouldn't allow anyone to approach it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.53,0:23:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他们远离那里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And so they kept away.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.34,0:23:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们将慢速舰拆除\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The slow ship was scuttled…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.88,0:23:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用它的框架和零件建造庇护所\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a refuge built from its bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.64,0:23:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经神秘的地方成为日常的场所\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And what was once mysterious became mundane.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.52,0:23:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的老师们说她很难教导\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Her teachers say she's difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.57,0:23:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是边缘人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's an outsider.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.24,0:23:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.45,0:23:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没用心听我的话 阿巴斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're not listening to me, Abbas.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.99,0:23:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是一个梦想者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's a dreamer.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.24,0:24:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她分心了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's distracted.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.04,0:24:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是一个思考者 和你一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's a thinker, like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.25,0:24:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她并没有分心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's not distracted.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.09,0:24:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是心无旁骛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.97,0:24:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看她 她对它着迷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just look at her. She's fascinated by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.39,0:24:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它很美\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.98,0:24:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它很危险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.31,0:24:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为里面有什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you think's inside it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.19,0:24:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.15,0:24:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你怎么知道它很危险 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then how do you know it's dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.57,0:24:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.53,0:24:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（现在）
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.14,0:25:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.02,0:25:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞得远远的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.52,0:26:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一天你会吓到我 到时你就惨了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One of these days you'll get me, and you'll be so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.24,0:26:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看起来很精神嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're looking good.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.40,0:26:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 穿着很搭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, coordinated.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.91,0:26:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-哪些地方搭了  -右靴和左靴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Which parts? -Right boot with left boot.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.20,0:26:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我居然没发现\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How did I miss that?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.58,0:26:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野外工作的进展如何 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How goes the wild work?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.50,0:26:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚在高地那边巡逻回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just got back from patrolling the highlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.54,0:26:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苔藓床的面积在缩小 冰鹭已经南飞了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lichen beds are shrinking. Ice lunes are already heading south.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.58,0:26:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意味着我们将迎来暖春\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Means we're gonna have a nice warm spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.54,0:26:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会想念这一切吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me you don't miss it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.75,0:26:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想念什么 硫磺的臭味 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What, the stench of sulfur?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.80,0:27:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冻疮 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the frostbite?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.88,0:27:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你比我更适合当守卫者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nah, being a warden suits you a lot better than it ever did me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.56,0:27:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 这只很大啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wow. That's a big one, hey?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.68,0:27:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 母主教爪 可能有600公斤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. Bishop's claw, female. Maybe 600 kilos.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.40,0:27:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去几周的深夜 它一直试图突破围栏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's been testing the fence late at night the last few weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.40,0:27:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给它命名为梅宝 它总是单独行动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna call her Maybel. She's a loner.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.49,0:27:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞佛 你为什么一大清早叫我来这里 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Salvor, why have you got me out here at this time in the morning, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.70,0:27:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道自己的女儿是在拖延时间 说吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know when my daughter's procrastinating. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.96,0:27:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了一个小测试\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I did a little test.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.92,0:27:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空域有些不对劲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Something's wrong with the null field.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.25,0:27:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么选择在此时测试 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And what made you check it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.13,0:27:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 一种感觉 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know. A feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.01,0:27:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我测试了 我获得证据了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I checked it out. I got evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.93,0:27:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 你告诉她了吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course. And have you told her yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.89,0:27:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想先让你知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wanted you to know first.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.31,0:27:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 但这事应该告诉她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I appreciate that. But it is for her to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.52,0:27:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并强调你有证据\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And stress the evidence part.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.18,0:28:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了谢顿博士的工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks to the efforts of Dr. Seldon,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.60,0:28:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里昂12世建造了我们的庇护所\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cleon XII established our refuge…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.35,0:28:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在计时方面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In terms of timekeeping,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.64,0:28:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水钟更加准确\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the water clock is the more precise instrument.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.98,0:28:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 但那需要水才能运行吧 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right. But it also requires water to work, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.61,0:28:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显然如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.98,0:28:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔德修士 水用光了怎么办 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What happens when the water runs out, Novice Jord?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.32,0:28:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果用日晷 我们只需要晷针 也就是突出来的叶片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For a sundial, all you need is the gnomon. That's the blade sticking out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.28,0:28:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然还需要…太阳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And, of course… the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.41,0:28:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里谢顿将灭亡后重建文明的任务 托付于我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hari Seldon entrusted us with rebuilding civilization after the collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.62,0:28:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能假设任何事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can't assume anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.92,0:29:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能假定未来的幸存者必能识字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whether or not our future survivors will be able to read,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.42,0:29:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或他们将说什么语言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or what language they'll speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.80,0:29:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们甚至不知道他们将分布在哪些星球\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We don't even know what worlds they'll be scattered upon.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.68,0:29:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他们身处天鹅座元星\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What if they find themselves on Cygnus Prime,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.10,0:29:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而唯一的水源来自泣藤呢 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}where the only moisture to be gained is from weeping vines?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.39,0:29:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 这座水钟确实更准确\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, yes, this water clock is more precise,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.27,0:29:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但日晷更实用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but the sundial is more practical.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.02,0:29:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们无法为后代将面临的每一个环境 或特殊状况做准备\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can't provide for every condition or contingency our descendants will face.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.86,0:29:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同理 我们不能保存每一项发明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}By the same token, we can't preserve every innovation,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.40,0:29:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们必须选择 并一直做出各种选择\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so we have to choose and keep choosing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.45,0:29:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到灭亡的那天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Until the fall comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.58,0:29:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会选水钟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd have picked the water clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.49,0:29:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你还在这里受训 那你确实有权选择\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you could have, if you were still training here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.25,0:29:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 这么说…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry, that was--
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.83,0:29:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你现在的职务很适合你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know you're suited to where you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.46,0:29:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保卫大家的平安 确保基地存活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}keeping us safe, making sure the Foundation survives--
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.63,0:29:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是确保你能存活 基地…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm making sure you survive. The Foundation--
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.50,0:29:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是同一件事 我们就是基地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's the same thing. We are the Foundation.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.51,0:29:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是 但你有信念 那很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am not. But you believe. And that is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.72,0:29:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 别把基地说得像邪教一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. Do not make this sound like a cult.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.64,0:29:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这一代人知道 真正的狂热教徒是怎样的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some of us in our generation know what real religious fervor looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.97,0:29:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想不想知道 我来是想告诉你什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you even wanna know what I came to tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.56,0:30:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我不喜欢靠近它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know I don't like being near it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.61,0:30:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸说你会想要证据 所以你必须亲自来看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dad said you'd want evidence, and this you gotta experience for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.78,0:30:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空域正在扩大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The null field is expanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.53,0:30:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空域原本从那里开始 现在延伸到这里了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The field used to start there. Now it starts here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.54,0:30:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果它继续扩大 我们也许需要让镇上的人撤离\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If it keeps expanding, we might need to clear out the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.90,0:30:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得第一次在这里发现你时的场景\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I remember the first time I found you out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.82,0:30:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时你四岁 半夜里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Four years old, middle of the night,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.78,0:30:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站在它的下方 仿佛…不受任何影响\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}standing right under it like it was… nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.66,0:31:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你的名字 你不转身\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you wouldn't turn when I called your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.33,0:31:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 我以为它在呼唤我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I thought it was calling to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.46,0:31:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽灵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.38,0:31:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像一位想象中的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Like an imaginary friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.38,0:31:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我伏在地上 试图爬到你身边 但是痛感太强烈了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I lay on the ground and tried to crawl to you, but the pain was too great.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.64,0:31:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You just…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.06,0:31:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}looked at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.93,0:31:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂为什么穹窿能伤到你 却伤不到我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I couldn't understand why the Vault was hurting you but not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.44,0:31:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是特别的 塞佛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're special, Salvor.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.98,0:31:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直都是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You always have been.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.69,0:31:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么要保密 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then why keep it a secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.16,0:31:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的父亲和我不想让别人对你差别对待\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your father and I didn't want people treating you differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.58,0:31:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 但是他们确实这么做了 妈妈 一直都是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, but they do, Mom. They always have.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.17,0:31:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我让他们感到不舒服\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I make them uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.21,0:31:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像穹窿一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just like the Vault.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.54,0:31:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它此刻在呼唤你吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is it calling to you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.59,0:31:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有用言语\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not in words.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.97,0:31:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我看证据吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Make your case.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.14,0:31:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得它正在苏醒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think it's waking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.27,0:32:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和其他的百科全书撰写者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You and the other encyclopedists,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.85,0:32:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在为遥远的危机未雨绸缪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you've been preparing for some distant crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.65,0:32:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我认为危机已经到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I think it's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.11,0:32:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在此时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.61,0:32:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉雅 凯尔 雨果来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gia! Keir! Guys, Hugo's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.83,0:32:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-雨果来了 -雨果来了…快去呀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Hugo's here! -Hugo's here! Hugo's here, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.66,0:32:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-雨果来了 -来呀 雨果\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Hugo's here! -Come on, Hugo!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.91,0:32:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-雨果 -雨果\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Hugo! -Hugo!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.46,0:32:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨果\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hugo!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.04,0:32:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快瞧 走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whoa. Look at that! Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.18,0:32:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-从这边走更快 -嘿 小心 嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Cut through this way! -Whoa. Hey, now. Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.18,0:32:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你捉不住我 -从这边走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Oh, you can't get me. -Through here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.06,0:32:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点 大家 快去 走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, guys. Come on. Hurry up! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.31,0:32:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波利 快跑 快点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Poly, come on! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.94,0:32:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨果…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hugo! Hugo!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.95,0:32:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-雨果 -雨果\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Hugo! -Hugo!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.07,0:32:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庄严发誓 雨果\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Four-sworn, Hugo!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.24,0:33:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女士们 先生们 你们几位大人需要我帮些什么忙 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gentlemen, ladies. What can I do for you grown adults?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.66,0:33:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我们带东西了吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Got anything for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.00,0:33:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克雷尔巧克力 慢用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Korellian chocolate. Knock yourselves out.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.00,0:33:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不想要巧克力 有啤酒吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We don't want chocolate. How about some beer?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.79,0:33:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你的胸口长毛了再问我要酒喝吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How about you come back and see me when you got hair on your chest?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.92,0:33:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别像无助的小宝宝一样乞求我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And don't come begging for it like wayward puppies.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.80,0:33:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们才不是乞求 我们是交易\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're not begging. We're… trading.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.13,0:33:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 拿什么交易 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that so? What for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.14,0:33:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们幽默的话语和有趣的陪伴 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How about our sparkling wit and company?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.56,0:33:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没兴趣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hard pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.10,0:33:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell you what.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.27,0:33:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你们几个小崽子帮我卸行李\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you clowns could help me load out,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.36,0:33:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许我能给你们找一些 与你们的年龄相符的玩意儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I might be able to scrounge up something a little more age-appropriate for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.32,0:33:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成交 我愿意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Deal. I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.11,0:33:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都愿意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We all will.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.28,0:33:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go on then.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.36,0:33:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-走吧 -走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Come on, guys. -Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.86,0:33:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-凯尔 接住 波利 -我在这边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Keir, catch. Poly. -I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.55,0:33:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好臭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That smells terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.21,0:33:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 这是用在橡胶靴上的密封剂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It should. It's sealant for my gum boots.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.97,0:34:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洋葱比我想的更多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}More onions than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.22,0:34:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能拿错食谱了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I may have used the wrong recipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.01,0:34:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就太不幸了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That would be a tragic mishap.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.77,0:34:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It'll keep.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.81,0:34:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么问题吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.69,0:34:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的厨房里有个男人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's a man in my kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.24,0:34:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这次待多久 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How long are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.24,0:34:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,29个漫长的小时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Twenty-nine long hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.28,0:34:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星系其他地方怎么样 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And how's the rest of the galaxy?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.24,0:34:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, it's big.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.95,0:34:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有空应该去看看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You should see it sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.50,0:34:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Should I?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.13,0:34:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳娜四号星\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Irina Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.47,0:34:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一片大陆 但全都是热带\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Only one continent, but it's tropical all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.68,0:34:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里的昆虫和狗一样大 也同样黏人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's got bugs the size of dogs and just as cuddly.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.18,0:34:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把药品留下了 带走了水果\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dropped off medicine, I picked up fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.35,0:34:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是任性供应商的流浪生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Such is the itinerant life of the wayward purveyor.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.31,0:34:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你把水果送去哪里了  -长庚星\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Where'd you take the fruit? -To Hesperus.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.86,0:34:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对它的了解已经和我差不多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which you could describe as well as me by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.40,0:35:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我偶然去到一个星团\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I was off on a whirlwind tour of this little cluster.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.53,0:35:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们开始交易之后就停不下来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Once they started trading, they couldn't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.70,0:35:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工人 糖 朗姆酒和现金的四边交易\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Little rectangular situation of workers and sugar, rum, cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.21,0:35:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你觉得自己的星球有很多卫星 你应该见识一下他们的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You think you've got a handful of moons, you should see what they got.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.46,0:35:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空像是洒满了硬币\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The sky looks like spilled coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.63,0:35:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洒满了硬币 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Spilled coins? -Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.46,0:35:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还真想看看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd love to see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.01,0:35:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该去看看 离开这个冰球\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, you need to go. Get off this ball of ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.26,0:35:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我在这里有责任 -但这不是你的选择\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I've got responsibilities here. -Oh, but you didn't pick them.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.39,0:35:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 但那仍是我的责任 而且…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nah, they're still mine. And…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.02,0:35:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能知道存在原因 但却不知道原因是什么吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is it possible to know you've got reasons and not know what they are?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.60,0:35:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对这个星球而言很重要的原因 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Reasons you're important to this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.48,0:35:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能 这么想有点自大 但有可能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's possible. A little egotistical, but possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.82,0:35:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的意思不是我很重要 我是说我不能离开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't say I was important. I said I can't leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.20,0:35:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到离开 你想现在吃晚餐还是之后再吃 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Speaking of leaving, would you like dinner now or after?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.33,0:35:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}After sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.47,0:36:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.68,0:36:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了什么问题吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.06,0:36:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是有种奇怪的感觉 我去边界附近走走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just a weird feeling. I'm gonna walk the perimeter.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.06,0:36:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为奇怪的感觉来自那里 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What, because that's where the weird feeling is coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.86,0:37:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那感觉来自这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, that is in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.48,0:37:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是散散步\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is just a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.86,0:37:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以如果我说 “等我穿好裤子” 你会说什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So if I said, "Let me get my pants," you'd say?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.45,0:37:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来的25个小时不准穿裤子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No pants for the next 25 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.66,0:37:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你等下会生气吗  -不会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Will you be mad later? -Never.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.48,0:37:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那里做什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you doing out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.90,0:37:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.16,0:37:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下 现在是宵禁时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stop. It's after curfew.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.39,0:38:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人吗 有人在吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello? Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.42,0:38:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.60,0:39:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.52,0:39:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听到枪声 怎么了 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I heard a shot. What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.10,0:39:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是疯了吗 那艘船像是安纳克里昂的 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Am I crazy, or is that ship Anacreon?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.90,0:39:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的确是疯子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, you're crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.65,0:39:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你说得没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But not about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.96,0:40:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在有三艘了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And then there are three.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.17,0:40:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-呼叫他们 -我们已经这么做了 没有回应\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Hail them. -We already have. No answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.58,0:40:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们也不理会我们的进近矢量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And they're ignoring our approach vectors.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.71,0:40:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们应该派一辆穿梭机去见他们吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Should we send one of our shuttles to meet them?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.67,0:40:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未装配武器的穿梭机 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your unarmed shuttles?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.05,0:40:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些可是护卫舰 武装飞船\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Those are corvettes. Gunships.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.51,0:40:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他怎么在这 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why is he here?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.89,0:40:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他知道武装飞船长什么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because he knows what gunships look like.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.97,0:40:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他是狄斯比斯人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Also, he's Thespin.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.39,0:40:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从爆炸事件后就离开了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Been off-world since the bombings.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.43,0:40:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 那样的话 你…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Impossible. That would make you--
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.02,0:40:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快70岁了 但我有一半的时间 都是在传送点间冷冻睡眠中度过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pushing 70. But I spent half that cryosleeping between ports.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.90,0:40:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去安纳克里昂送货的时候 外星的身份比较有利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When you tow freight to Anacreon, it pays to be blood-neutral.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.23,0:40:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-安纳克里昂受帝国制裁 -成熟点吧 路易斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Anacreon is under imperial sanction. -Grow up, Lewis.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.82,0:40:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许只是个意外 也许他们偏离航道了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe it's a mistake. Maybe they wandered off course.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.87,0:40:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们根本就是想趁我们不注意偷偷着陆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're literally trying to sneak in under our radar.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.87,0:40:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这是一个科学哨站 没有任何有价值的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We are a scientific outpost. We have nothing of value here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.04,0:40:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市长 安纳克里昂人 曾在本星球着陆过吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mayor, have the Anacreons ever made landfall here before?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.66,0:40:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有安纳克里昂人 也没有狄斯比斯人 30年来没有任何人着陆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No Anacreons, no Thespins. No one in 30 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.58,0:40:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据帝国法令 他们一概不得踏足端点星\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Under imperial edict, Terminus is off-limit to all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.46,0:40:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一定与穹窿有关\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's gotta be connected to the Vault.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.13,0:40:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.34,0:40:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空域正在扩大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The null field's expanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.22,0:40:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我昨天发现了 -速度多快 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I noticed it yesterday. -How fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.64,0:40:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天 安纳克里昂人就出现了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The next day, the Anacreons showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.47,0:41:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,严格来说 我们是帝国哨站\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Technically, we are an imperial outpost.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.10,0:41:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都知道安纳克里昂跟帝国有过节\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And Lord knows the Anacreons have a bone to pick with the Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.56,0:41:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是穹窿也许是安纳克里昂…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you suggesting the Vault might be an Anacreon--
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.77,0:41:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的意思是穹窿知道些什么并作出了反应\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm suggesting the Vault knew something and reacted.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.19,0:41:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许它甚至曾提醒我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe it even warned us.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.52,0:41:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说穹窿向你发信号了 因为你与众不同 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you saying the Vault was signaling you because you're somehow, what, special?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.32,0:41:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞佛是一个异类\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Salvor is an outlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.53,0:41:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须想一想计划是否预测到…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need to think whether the Plan could have possibly predicted--
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.24,0:41:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了计划吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Forget the Plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.62,0:41:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢顿已经不在了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seldon's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.83,0:41:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们什么时候才会开始独立思考 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When are any of you gonna start thinking for yourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.87,0:41:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 够了 我们不需要把情况弄得复杂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, that's enough. We don't need to make this complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.17,0:41:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安纳克里昂不理会我们的呼叫 他们侵犯了帝国领空\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Anacreons have ignored our hails, and they are violating imperial aerospace.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.59,0:41:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们很清楚该采取什么行动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our course of action is obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.59,0:41:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们将上连通讯浮标\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll uplink to the communications buoy
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.47,0:41:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到达下一个自转通讯空窗期时就这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as soon as we hit the next rotational window.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.26,0:41:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们呼叫帝国 他们将派人来这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll call the Empire, and they will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.27,0:41:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.94,0:41:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去查看军械库\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To check out the armory.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.94,0:41:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果安纳克里昂人先于帝国援兵到达\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If the Anacreons come knocking before the Empire,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.40,0:41:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道我们能集合多少武力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd like to know what kind of violence we can muster.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.11,0:41:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有多久没有检查这些了 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When was the last time these were broken down?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.95,0:42:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我们只是有点懈怠 -如果需要 我有一把离子手枪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-So we're a little complacent. -I've got an ion pistol, if that helps.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.70,0:42:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 策展店里有什么用得上的东西 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mom, anything we could use in the curation stores?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.70,0:42:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几把手斧 一条纺织者星的牧羊人投石带\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A few hand axes, a shepherd's sling from Weaver's World.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.37,0:42:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我不应松懈的 -这不是你的职责所在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I should've been on top of this. -Not your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.62,0:42:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不是吗 我该确保你们的安全 记得吗  -来…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-No? I keep you safe, remember? -Come on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.33,0:42:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种时刻 我一般建议喝点酒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Generally I propose alcohol at a juncture like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.88,0:42:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（通讯连接 帝国编解码器启动）
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.42,0:42:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通讯空窗期到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rotational window's open.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.26,0:42:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,握手协议 只需几秒钟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Handshake protocol. It just takes a few seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.06,0:42:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（通讯连接失败）
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.73,0:42:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.98,0:42:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通讯浮标没有回应我们的任何呼叫 失去信号了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Comms buoy's not responding to any of our pings. It's gone dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.99,0:42:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换一个试试\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Use another one then.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.28,0:42:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有其他的了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There isn't another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.66,0:42:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说这意味着什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, what does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.45,0:42:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们无法联络上帝国\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can't contact the Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.20,0:42:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续尝试联络 别慌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, keep trying. Don't panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.71,0:42:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许只是因为流星雨 会过去的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Could be something as simple as a meteor shower. It'll clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.83,0:42:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恰好在安纳克里昂飞越之后 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On the heels of an Anacreon flyby?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.55,0:42:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假设安纳克里昂人计划在这里着陆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Assuming the Anacreons intend landfall here,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.17,0:42:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们还有多久会到达 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}how long before they arrive?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.67,0:43:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据他们现在的进近状态 我认为还要40个小时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Based on their current approach, I'd say another 40 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.56,0:43:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.64,0:43:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.60,0:43:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心理历史学\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Psychohistory.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.02,0:43:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里的所有研究 以数学等式的形式表现\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All of Hari's work expressed as a mathematical equation.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.53,0:44:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我在他葬礼后的那晚从他办公室拿走的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I took it from his office the night after his funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.07,0:44:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的计算结果为我们 进行这一切工作的原因提供了理据\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His numbers are the basis for why we do what we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.87,0:44:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞船上原本有两个人能够真正理解它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On the ship, there were two people who could actually understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.08,0:44:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里谢顿和盖尔多尼克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hari Seldon and Gaal Dornick.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.34,0:44:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能理解它吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you make anything of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.80,0:44:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 不太可能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Me? No, not likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.13,0:44:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞佛 如果你是计划的一部分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Salvor, if you were part of the Plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.43,0:44:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我会更容易相信这一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it would make it a lot easier for me to believe in all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.63,0:45:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不奇怪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, well, big surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.64,0:45:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值得一试\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was worth a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.76,0:45:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值得吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.68,0:45:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你说过 不同不意味着特别\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I told you, different's not the same as special.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.24,0:45:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通讯浮标出故障了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Comms buoy is down.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.41,0:45:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是不祥的预兆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That is an ominous happenstance.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.75,0:45:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最好还是离开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You should probably hightail it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.54,0:45:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.30,0:45:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安纳克里昂人两天后就会到达 也许更快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Anacreons will be here in two days. Maybe less.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.51,0:45:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去任何地方都比这里安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You would be safer anywhere but here.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.64,0:45:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每年此时的风景都很美\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The scenery is so beautiful this time of year.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.43,0:45:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一望无际的废墟 满是冰冻的鹭粪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Vast wastelands of frozen lune shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.85,0:45:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是认真的 雨果\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm serious, Hugo.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.14,0:45:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一向都是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You tend to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.56,0:46:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪都不去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.82,0:46:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是属于你的战役\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This isn't your fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.23,0:46:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那是谁的 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, yeah? Whose fight is it then?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.41,0:46:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢顿的 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seldon's?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.45,0:46:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么也不是你的战役\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then it's not your fight either.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.83,0:46:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起离开吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come away with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.25,0:46:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.34,0:46:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.30,0:46:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我必须保护他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because I have to protect them.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.64,0:46:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活着即意味着与幽灵相伴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To be alive is to know ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.93,0:46:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝国忌惮哈里 因为他能够预知未来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Empire feared Hari because he could forecast the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.85,0:46:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但事实上他做的不过是重新检视过去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But, in reality, all he was doing was reexamining the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.57,0:46:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.74,0:46:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意观察规律 我们就能预测接下来将发生的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pay attention to the patterns and we can presage what comes next.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.41,0:47:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活着即意味着与幽灵相伴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To be alive is to know ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.58,0:47:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果用心听 我们能听见幽灵的低语\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We hear their whispers if we listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.86,0:47:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You again.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.89,0:47:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey there.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.10,0:48:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么伤到你了 梅宝 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What got you, Maybel?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.49,0:48:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有点疼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is gonna hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.30,0:48:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别紧张\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.09,0:48:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放下武器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Drop your weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.97,0:48:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.10,0:48:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞佛哈定 端点星的守卫者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Salvor Hardin, warden of Terminus.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.86,0:48:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安纳克里昂人不得进入帝国的领土\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anacreons aren't allowed on imperial soil.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.28,0:48:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来这里做什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.32,0:49:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亡者的幽灵出没于 我们旧日家园的废墟中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The ghosts of the dead haunt the skeletons that were once our homes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.79,0:49:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们环绕着我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They surround us.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.46,0:49:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们对我们所拥有的一切虎视眈眈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And they're hungry for what's ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.60,0:50:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,字幕翻译：易晗